#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"a) The Club has a bar where players can grab something to eat between games "
"or have a beer.<br/>\n"
"            It can be accessed in\n"
"            <strong>\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Point of Sales &gt; Bar </"
"font><font class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">and "
"contains some basic products.</span></font>\n"
"            </strong>\n"
"            <br/>\n"
"            Customers can pay by through different means, including by "
"adding the note to their account."
msgstr ""
"a) Klubben har en bar, hvor spillerne kan få noget at spise mellem kampene "
"eller drikke en øl.<br/>\n"
"            Den kan tilgås i\n"
"           <strong>\n"
"                <font class=\"text-o-color-1\"> POS &gt; Bar </font><font "
"class=\"text-black\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"> og indeholder "
"nogle basale produkter.</span></font>\n"
"           </strong>\n"
"            <br/> \n"
"            Kunderne kan betale på forskellige måder, blandt andet ved at "
"indbetale penge på deres konto."

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.homepage
msgid "and get started!&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr "og kom i gang!&amp;nbsp;"

#. module: sports_club
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:sports_club.welcome_article_body
